{"tid":2282502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DQ 議員後立法會續會    熱血公民鄭松泰發言十分鐘即離去","createTime":"2020-11-12T02:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T10:26:08.000Z","uid":50386,"like":92,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"796eeffab6a6f2f425033748dbf2d8ca02e1daa8","tid":2282502,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:03:03.000Z","msg":"港府跟隨全國人大常委決定，昨宣布 DQ 四名民主派立法會議員，全體民主派随即表態總辭，惟醫學界議員陳沛然和熱血公民鄭松泰宣布不會跟隨，二人繼續留任，成為現時立法會僅餘的非建制派。<br />\n<br />\n立法會今（12 日）續會，鄭松泰首位發言，完成有關季節性流感疫苗的口頭質詢後，約十分鐘即離開議事廳。至於昨日原本表示會到議事廳遞辭職信的民主派，後來臨時取消行動，沒有民主派議員出席會議。"},{"pid":"31abcbcd586bfea56c167f1dddfd078cff2d20de","tid":2282502,"uid":72085,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:04:38.000Z","msg":"熱血公民最大在野黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8142ddafee86728670e16beea4d06ac94fb2db","tid":2282502,"uid":2471,"like":40,"dislike":8,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:04:54.000Z","msg":"泰博都係做自己野 支持"},{"pid":"024a6f6c7601947f45599cce6b566b7564429752","tid":2282502,"uid":152476,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:05:09.000Z","msg":"好勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eaf2a0425f129d2237fc0f050b776b686e9a29a","tid":2282502,"uid":19528,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:05:16.000Z","msg":"支持熱狗 🌭️ 死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45a46cea124463cb6a26eb41fc98207aea86f53","tid":2282502,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"024a6f6c7601947f45599cce6b566b7564429752","tid":2282502,"uid":152476,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:05:09.000Z","msg":"好勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"好忠誠"},{"pid":"e6ed42552ccef230d605fc4421deddf24a7d5ff8","tid":2282502,"uid":383914,"like":6,"dislike":2,